text: cng klaw theid chan ca yudthux “phu khumkhrxng xun ca kxallxhˌ kranan hrux” sung phraxngkh pen phu pradisʹth brrda chan fa læa phændin læa phraxngkh pen phuthrng hı xahar læa mi thuk hı xahar cng klaw theid(muhammad) thæcring chan thuk chı hı pen khn ræk nı hmu thi swamiphakdi læa phwk than cng xya xyu nı hmu phu hı mi phakhi penxankhad
